---
import StudyList from '../containers/StudyList.astro';

---

<section id="about" class="p-2 md:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-center text-2xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-white">Sobre <span class="text-cyan-400">Mi</span></h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse gap-y-4 py-2 md:py-12 items-center justify-center lg:flex-row md:justify-around">
        <div class="dimension bg-gray-800 rounded-xl md:rounded-3xl flex justify-center items-center shadow-slate-600 shadow-xl">
            <img src="/images/IMG-20221117-WA0011.jpg" alt="foto de perfil del candidato" class="rounded-xl" width="70%">
        </div>
        <div class="m-4 lg:w-6/12 flex flex-col gap-y-5">
            <p class="text-cyan-400 md:text-xl font-semibold">Me considero una persona divertida,carismatico y siempre estoy en constante aprendizaje de nuevas herramientas</p>
            <div>
                <p class="text-base md:text-xl font-semibold md:py-2 text-cyan-400">Cuidad: <span class="text-white">CABA, Buenos Aires - Argentina</span></p>
                <p class="text-base md:text-xl font-semibold md:py-2 text-cyan-400">Correo: <span class="text-white">eduardoetolaba@gmail.com</span></p>
                <p class="text-base md:text-xl font-semibold md:py-2 text-cyan-400">Edad: <span class="text-white">22 a√±os</span></p>
            </div>
            <button class="text-cyan-400 border-2 border-cyan-400 p-2 text-xs md:text-base lg:text-xl font-bold rounded-lg m-auto hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-cyan-500 hover:bg-cyan-400 hover:text-zinc-900"><a href="#">Descargar CV</a></button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <StudyList/>
</section>

<style>
.dimension{
    width: 420px;
    height: 420px;
}
@media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
    .dimension{
        width: 320px;
        height: 320px;
    }
}
</style>